               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="16r">1v-16r</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s8IHA">قران, First ǧuz’ (1/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#2v">-2v</locus>سورة الفاتحة للكتاب سبع ابات بسم الله الرّحمن الرّحيم<note>Title of the Sura rubricated.</note>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#16r">-16r</locus>وَلَكُمْ مَا كَسَبْتُمْ وَلَاتُسْئَلُوْنَ عَمَّا كَانُوْا يَعْمَلُوْنَ</explicit>
                     <note>1:1-2:141. On fol. 1v, titles of sūras in red traced in black. Red and black ǧuz' marker on fol. 1v. Red commas as verse markers. Words completed on the following line. Deletions. Correction by another hand in the margin of fol. 7r.  </note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
